These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, pumpkin
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | fanta  | coffee |
| Food       | nectarine | pumpkin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, 7up
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | cola | 7up |
| Sport      | rugby     | basketball  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, documentary
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, colombian
1. the dutch is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the dutch is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | documentary  |
| Nationality   | dutch | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
