There 2 different types of food: garlic, kale
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Beverage   | water | juice   |
| Food       | kale | garlic |

