.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, british
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goldfish
1. the british is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Nationality   | egyptian | british |
| Pet           | goldfish     | hedgehog  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, card-games
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, project-manager
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the project-manager is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | card-games | dancing |
| Job     | entrepreneur        | project-manager |

