.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-10::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, time-travel
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel   | disaster |
| Transport     | ship | boat    |

